name: supernova on the rocks
description:
this is a glb model of a supernova on the rocks.

surfaces made of vertices give us the ability to imagine objects, environments and worlds that we could not otherwise. There is a kind of speculative modeling that seems to spring from science fiction, and that uses reuse models, which when modified, seem to point to meanings that are absent in principle but seem to emerge from our unconscious.
